OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGrandad first in world to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftry sight-saving drug      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Merseyside grandad has become the    
OL,6, first person in the world to be given a
OL,7, new medication that could prevent him  
OL,8, from losing his eyesight.              
OL,10,FSteve Gotts, 63, who has lived with    
OL,11,Fdiabetes for 30 years, is receiving the
OL,12,Ftreatment at the Royal Liverpool       
OL,13,FUniversity Hospital as part of a trial.
OL,15,FHe has been given a tablet to reduce   
OL,16,Feffects of diabetic maculopathy.       
OL,18,FMr Gotts said the risk of going blind  
OL,19,Fand not seeing his grandchildren       
OL,20,Fgrow-up promoted him to take part.     
